betterquesting:10.desc:8:
This way for your first dimensions!

Magic can be done in any order, but the optional objective lists some good strategies!

When doing magic, bad things may happen. In order to minimize negative effects to your world, the following order should be followed, all other mods can be done earlier or later.
1. Start with blood magic, until unlocking the Ritual of Eldritch will. This will prevent flux from building up.
2. Start thaumcraft, until unlocking sanitizing soap. This will help out with temporary warp.
3. Go through abyssalcraft, collect the abyssal wasteland and dreadlands warp cleansers in the respective dimensions. They can be found in altars around the dimensions!
4. The omothol warp cleanser will completely eliminate the issue with warp!
5. Now you are protected, feel free to right-click a Really Scary Vishroom!
When it comes to other magic mods, feel free to progress though them in whichever way you prefer :)
